<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-12-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-12-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="147" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d147">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.51/1716</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                Minister <persName type="to">Reinsch</persName>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-12-05">
                                    <hi rend="italic">December 5, 1916</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Department’s telegram December 4. You are authorized to take occasion to
                            intimate to your colleagues representing Governments of group bankers’
                            nationalities that any strained construction of existing agreements
                            between the Chinese Government and bankers, or any attempt to exclude
                            our bankers from a fair participation in Chinese affairs, would meet
                            with very decided resistance from this Government.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>